{"tid":2401591,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呢單野咩事？全世界最大廣告公司都要爭住奶共？","createTime":"2021-02-10T00:32:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-10T05:51:08.000Z","uid":113951,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"75077f2a8a985e3a889646badfa2e5b002bd8c0c","tid":2401591,"uid":113951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T00:32:20.000Z","msg":"堂堂全世界最大廣告公司<br />\n成班鬼佬輪住擦抖音鞋<br />\n爭住幫垃圾支那app係美國做生意<br />\n真係睇見都核撚突<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢地唔驚最後被支那公司打開左市場之後用完即棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em>抖音宣佈將夥拍全球最大的廣告集團WPP，合作力攻美國市場，大推兩天前文章分析的那三種「短視頻」平台盈利模式。又不免見到一堆國際廣告界鬼佬高層輪番力讚抖音，場面真係非常嘔心。<br />\n<br />\n「打賞」一向是快手的重要收入，早年佔總收入近九成，上年頭三季中亦佔約六成，其餘為廣告收入(三成多)和主播賣貨抽佣(約5%)。</em><br />\n<br />\n多得拜登放生抖音<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em>雖然之前Trump任內力禁抖音在美國流行(或者最少先由美國公司控制)，可惜最後因為遇到深層國家操控的各地法院從中作梗，以致商務部未能中止抖音營運。但今日拜登上台，抖音就立即重新上路了。 <br />\n<br />\n2020年總統大選期間，更加成為「拜登數碼聯盟」的政治動員工具，破壞Trump的造勢大會，成功留位然後缺席的方式霸佔門票，令Trump支持者無法到場。</em><br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://mewe.com/p/blackmirrortech/show/601e06303fa4830cf8e3a867\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmewe.com%2Fp%2Fblackmirrortech%2Fshow%2F601e06303fa4830cf8e3a867&d=%2BlEHcpGCWp7P1IX%2BOWqMQs0oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=9045fca7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mewe.com/p/blackmirrortech/show/601e06303fa4830cf8e3a867</a>"},{"pid":"0762b01d801f95e91dab4a52619776bb4ac51486","tid":2401591,"uid":16061,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T00:42:28.000Z","msg":"美國都奶，公司算係咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b60c3578603f746fd749e5bee986545b710e555","tid":2401591,"uid":113951,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0762b01d801f95e91dab4a52619776bb4ac51486","tid":2401591,"uid":16061,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T00:42:28.000Z","msg":"美國都奶，公司算係咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T00:51:35.000Z","msg":"你又講得有道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"204a9bf61355891840cd637923de82eefbed4737","tid":2401591,"uid":113951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T01:45:50.000Z","msg":"呢條link先岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://mewe.com/p/blackmirrortech/show/6022a7457a916f575436ea0f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmewe.com%2Fp%2Fblackmirrortech%2Fshow%2F6022a7457a916f575436ea0f&d=%2BlEHcpGCWp7P1IX%2BOWqMQs0oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=8c24313f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mewe.com/p/blackmirrortech/show/6022a7457a916f575436ea0f</a>"},{"pid":"832e23d71d44b2fa4d276c5178c3c497c1ad5efa","tid":2401591,"uid":179409,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T04:49:19.000Z","msg":"有時換過角度睇<br />\n有機會見證支國逐步消滅美國<br />\n人類文明整體再次步入黑暗威權時代<br />\n都算不枉此生"},{"pid":"a76861874c5e03b042a8ed3b4afe965997797575","tid":2401591,"uid":113951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"832e23d71d44b2fa4d276c5178c3c497c1ad5efa","tid":2401591,"uid":179409,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedB